Hi all,

similar to the the append operator, +=, a prepend operator would
be useful. Of course, foo="blah$foo" would work just as well, but
a dedicated operator would look cleaner, imo.
I suggest the use of -=, but any other operator would be fine, as
well.


Thanks,
Richard

